  "subject": "Handle uncommon format of proper tar archive",
  "commit_message": "Handle uncommon format of proper tar archive\n\nProvide proper handling of tar archives containing\n\"current directory\", but stored in format:\n```\n.\nfile2.txt\ndir1/\ndir1/file1.txt\n```\ninstead of typical:\n```\n./\n./file2.txt\n./dir1/\n./dir1/file1.txt\n```\n\nIssue-ID: MULTICLOUD-1025\nSigned-off-by: Konrad Bańka <k.banka@samsung.com>\nChange-Id: Ideffd019255a9f2d029527066e5a6a03d45a2d7b\n",
